snippet.description:
Dark Half presents…”A Cult Shit Christmas” EP with new tracks by Dark Half, Majik Duce, DieaboliK The Monster, Bloody Ruckus and S.A.W. a.k.a. Yung Ghozt!!

This EP was mixed and mastered by SKR’s Sicktanick of thesickbeats.com except for Merry Cult Shit Christmas which was mixed by Void of Void Productionz and Black X-Mas which was mixed by DieaboliK The Monster!!

Track Listing:
01. Merry Cult Shit Christmas (Geno Cultshit ft. Bloody Ruckus)
02. Something in the Wind (Dark Half ft. S.A.W. a.k.a. Yung Ghozt)
03. The GingerDead Man (Damien Quinn a.k.a. Damien Jones)
04. Black X-Mas (DieaboliK The Monster)
05. Christmas Sucks (Dark Half ft. Majik Duce)
snippet.title: Dark Half - A Cult Shit Christmas EP - 01. Merry Cult Shit Xmas (Geno Cultshit ft. Bloody Ruckus)

Dark Half presents…”A Cult Shit Christmas” 3 with new tracks by "The Leatherface of Wisconsin" Damien Quinn, SKR's own Razakel, The New Jersey Devil and Cult Activity (Bloody Ruckus, S.A.W. Da Ghozt and Damien Quinn) featuring LSP's own Claas!!

This EP was mixed and mastered by SKR’s Sicktanick of thesickbeats.com except for "How The Grinch Murdered Christmas" which was mixed and mastered by The New Jerzey Devil!!

01. A Cult Shit Christmas Tale (Damien Quinn)
02. Stocking Stuffer (Razakel feat. Damien Quinn)
03. How The Grinch Murdered Christmas (New Jerzey Devil)
04. The Death Of Santa Claus (Cult Activity feat. Claas)
